msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Analysis Options"
msgstr "分析選項"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Here, options for the analysis can be specified."
msgstr "這裡可以指定分析的選項。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Rotation Method"
msgstr "轉軸方式"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"Here, the rotation method to apply to the components can be specified. "
"Rotation ensures a simpler understanding of the data structure."
msgstr ""
"這裡可以指定應用於各成分的旋轉方法。旋轉能夠讓資料結構的理解更加簡單明確。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Orthogonal"
msgstr "直交"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"This method produces components that are uncorrelated. For this method, "
"there are several possibilities that can be selected."
msgstr "此方法產出之成分間互不相關。針對此方法，可選用多種不同選項。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "none"
msgstr "無"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "No rotation method is selected."
msgstr "未選取任何轉軸方法。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"Maximizes the variance of squared loadings for each factor, simplifying "
"interpretations."
msgstr "最大化各因子平方負荷量之變異數，以簡化解釋。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"Minimizes the number of factors needed to explain each variable, simplifying "
"structure."
msgstr "最小化解釋各變項所需之因子數，以簡化結構。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"Orthogonal rotation method by Bentler, used for simplifying factor loadings."
msgstr "Bentler 提出之直交轉軸法，用於簡化因子負荷量。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"Combines Varimax and Quartimax to balance factor simplicity and variable "
"explanations."
msgstr "結合 Varimax 與 Quartimax，以平衡因子簡潔性與變項解釋力。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"Applies an orthogonal rotation minimizing a weighted sum of squared loadings."
msgstr "應用直交轉軸，最小化負荷量平方之加權和。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Oblique"
msgstr "斜交"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"This method produces components that allow for correlation between the "
"components. This method is selected by default. Several possibilities are "
"available. The default is promax."
msgstr ""
"此方法產出之成分間允許相關。此選項為預設選取，並提供多種選項，預設為 promax。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"Starts with Varimax and applies a power transformation to allow correlated "
"factors."
msgstr "始於 Varimax，再應用冪次轉換以允許因素間相關。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"An oblique rotation that minimizes the correlation among factors while "
"allowing flexibility."
msgstr "斜交轉軸法，在允許彈性之同時最小化因素間相關。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Aims to simplify factor loadings by minimizing nonzero entries."
msgstr "旨在透過最小化非零元素以簡化因素負荷量。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Oblique rotation by Bentler, simplifying factor correlations."
msgstr "Bentler 提出之斜交轉軸法，用於簡化因素相關。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"An oblique rotation balancing between simple and interpretable factor "
"loadings."
msgstr "斜交轉軸法，在簡潔性與可解釋性之因素負荷量間取得平衡。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"Targets a cluster rotation for factor analysis, emphasizing group separation."
msgstr "針對因素分析進行集群轉軸，強調群組分離。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"An oblique version of Geomin, allowing factor correlations and reducing "
"complex loadings."
msgstr "Geomin 之斜交版本，允許因素相關並減少複雜負荷量。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Base Decomposition on"
msgstr "依據...，而分解資料"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "What to base the decomposition of the data into components/factors on."
msgstr "將資料分解而成為萃取成分／因素時所依據的基礎。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Correlation matrix"
msgstr "相關矩陣"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"The correlation matrix is used to decompose the data into components/factors."
msgstr "使用相關矩陣將資料分解為成分／因素。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Covariance matrix"
msgstr "共變數矩陣"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"The covariance matrix is used to decompose the data into components/factors."
msgstr "使用共變數矩陣將資料分解為成分／因素。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Polychoric/tetrachoric correlation matrix"
msgstr "多序列相關／四分相關矩陣"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"The polychoric/tetrachoric correlation matrix is used to decompose the data "
"into components/factors. This is sometimes unstable when sample size is "
"small and when some variables do not contain all response categories"
msgstr ""
"使用多序列相關／四分相關矩陣將資料分解為成分／因素。此方法在樣本數較小，或部"
"分變項未包含所有反應類別時，可能出現不穩定之情況"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Factoring Method"
msgstr "萃取方法"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Which factoring method to use for the decomposition."
msgstr "用於分解資料的因素萃取方法。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Minimum residual"
msgstr "最小殘差法"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid ""
"Perform a minimum residual factor analysis (minres) using the first "
"derivative."
msgstr "使用一階導數進行最小殘差因素分析（minres）。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Maximum likelihood"
msgstr "最大概似法"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Perform a maximum likelihood factor analysis (ml)."
msgstr "執行最大概似因素分析（ml）。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Principal axis factoring"
msgstr "主軸因素法"

msgctxt "PcaEfaAnalysisOptions|"
msgid "Perform a principal factor solution (pa)."
msgstr "執行主因素解法（pa）。"

