msgctxt "PcaEfaNumberFactors|"
msgid "Number of Components"
msgstr "成分的個數"

msgctxt "PcaEfaNumberFactors|"
msgid "Number of Factors"
msgstr "因素的個數"

msgctxt "PcaEfaNumberFactors|"
msgid ""
"Here, the number of components/factors that are used in the analysis is "
"determined. Several methods to determine this number can be chosen from:"
msgstr ""
"這裡將決定在分析中所使用的成分／因素數量。可從多種方法中選擇來決定這個數量："

msgctxt "PcaEfaNumberFactors|"
msgid "Based on"
msgstr "基於何種方法："

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaNumberFactors|"
msgid "Parallel analysis"
msgstr "平行分析法"

msgctxt "PcaEfaNumberFactors|"
msgid ""
"Components/factors are selected on the basis of parallel analysis. With this "
"method, factors are selected when their eigenvalue is greater than the "
"parallel average random eigenvalue. This method is selected by default. Can "
"be based on principal component eigenvalues (PC) or factor eigenvalues (FA). "
"A seed (1234) is chosen by default so that the results from the parallel "
"analysis are equal across the PCA"
msgstr ""
"成分／因素之選取係依據平行分析。此方法選取特徵值大於平行平均隨機特徵值之因"
"素，為預設選項。可依據主成分特徵值（PC）或因素特徵值（FA）進行選取。預設種子"
"數（1234）可確保平行分析結果在主成分分析中具有可重複性"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaNumberFactors|"
msgid "Based on PC"
msgstr "主成分"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaNumberFactors|"
msgid "Based on FA"
msgstr "因素"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaNumberFactors|"
msgid "Eigenvalues"
msgstr "特徵值"

msgctxt "PcaEfaNumberFactors|"
msgid ""
"Components are selected when they have a certain eigenvalue. By default "
