"variables, meaning according to their occurence in the variables list."
msgstr ""
"可以將負荷量依大小由大到小排序，或依變數排序，也就是按照變數清單中的出現順序"
"排列。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Size"
msgstr "負荷量大小"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
