msgstr "變項"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Tables"
msgstr "表格"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Display addition tables in the output."
msgstr "於輸出結果中顯示額外表格。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Structure matrix"
msgstr "結構矩陣"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid ""
"An item by factor structure matrix. This is just the loadings (pattern) "
"matrix times the factor intercorrelation matrix."
msgstr "項目與因素之結構矩陣。此為負荷量（型態）矩陣乘以因子間相關矩陣之結果。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Component correlations"
msgstr "成分相關性"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Factor correlations"
msgstr "因素相關係數"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid ""
"When selecting this option, a table with the correlations between the "
"components/factors will be displayed."
msgstr "選取此選項時，將顯示成分／因素間之相關矩陣表格。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Additional fit indices"
msgstr "其他配適指標"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid ""
"This option displays the Root Mean Squared Error of Approximation (RMSEA) "
"with 90% confidence interval, the Tucker Lewis Index (TLI), and the Bayesian "
"Information Criterion (BIC) to test the fit of the model."
msgstr ""
"此選項顯示模型適配度檢定指標，包括均方根誤差近似值（RMSEA）及其90%信賴區間、"
"Tucker-Lewis指數（TLI）以及貝葉斯資訊準則（BIC）。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Residual matrix"
msgstr "殘差矩陣"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Displays a table containing the residual variances and correlations."
msgstr "顯示包含殘差變異數與相關係數之表格。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Parallel analysis"
msgstr "平行分析法"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, a table will be generated exhibiting a detailed "
"output of the parallel analysis. Can be based on principal component "
"eigenvalues (PC) or factor eigenvalues (FA). The seed is taken from the "
"parallel analysis for determining the number of components/factors above."
msgstr ""
"勾選此選項後，將生成一個表格，顯示平行分析的詳細輸出。可基於主成分特徵值"
"（PC）或因子特徵值（FA）。隨機種子取自上述用於決定成分／因子數量的平行分析。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Based on PC"
msgstr "主成分"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Based on FA"
msgstr "因素"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Plots"
msgstr "圖"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Display plots."
msgstr "顯示圖形。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Path diagram"
msgstr "路徑圖"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid ""
"By selecting this option, a visual representation of the direction and "
"strength of the relation between the variable and factor will be displayed."
msgstr "選取此選項時，將顯示變數與因子間關係方向與強度之視覺化呈現。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Scree plot"
msgstr "陡坡圖"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid ""
"When selecting this option, a scree plot will be displayed. The scree plot "
"provides information on how much variance in the data, indicated by the "
"eigenvalue, is explained by each factor. A scree plot can be used to decide "
"how many factors should be selected."
msgstr ""
"選取此選項時，將顯示陡坡圖。陡坡圖提供各因素所解釋之資料變異量（以特徵值表"
"示）之資訊，可用於決定應選取之因素個數。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Parallel analysis results"
msgstr "平行分析結果"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid ""
"Display the results of the parallel analysis in the scree plot. The parallel "
"analysis will be based on PC or FA as defined by the option for the parallel "
"analysis table."
msgstr ""
"於陡坡圖中顯示平行分析之結果。平行分析將依據平行分析表格選項所定義之 PC 或 "
"FA 進行。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Assumption checks"
msgstr "前提假設的檢驗"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid ""
"Assumptions: The variables included in the analysis are correlated; the "
"variables included in the analysis are linearly related (Shlens, 2014)"
msgstr ""
"假設條件：納入分析之變項間具有相關；納入分析之變項間呈線性關係（Shlens, "
"2014）"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "KMO test"
msgstr "KMO 檢定"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid ""
"Determines how well variables are suited for factor analysis by computing "
"the proportion of common variance between variables. Produces a measure of "
"sampling adequacy (MSA) as the proportion of common variance among variables "
"is computed for all variables; values closer to 1 are desired."
msgstr ""
"透過計算變項間共同變異之比例，評估變項是否適合進行因素分析。計算所有變項之取"
"樣適切性量數（MSA），即變項間共同變異之比例，數值越接近 1 越理想。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Bartlett's test"
msgstr "Bartlett's 球形檢定"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid ""
"Determines if the data correlation matrix is the identity matrix, meaning, "
"if the variables are related or not. A significant result means the "
"correlation matrix is unlike the identity matrix."
msgstr ""
"檢定資料之相關矩陣是否為單元矩陣，即判斷變項間是否存在關聯。檢定結果達顯著，"
"表示相關矩陣異於單元矩陣。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Mardia's test"
msgstr "Mardia's 檢定"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid ""
"Assesses the degree of the departure from multivariate normality of the "
"included variables in terms of multivariate skewness and kurtosis. The "
"Mardia's test will always include the listwise complete cases."
msgstr ""
"以多變量偏度與峰度評估納入變項偏離多變量常態分配之程度。Mardia 檢定將始終採用"
"完整案例進行分析。"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Anti-image correlation matrix"
msgstr "反映像相關矩陣"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid ""
"Contains the negative partial correlations between pairs of variables after "
"accounting for the effects of all other variables in the dataset. High "
"values in the anti-image correlation matrix indicate that a variable might "
"be redundant or have too much shared variance with other variables."
msgstr ""
"包含在控制資料集中所有其他變項之影響後，各變項對之間的反向偏相關。反映像相關"
"矩陣中數值較高，表示該變項可能與其他變項存在重疊或共享過多變異。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Missing Values"
msgstr "遺漏值"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Select how to handle missing values."
msgstr "選擇缺失值之處理方式。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Exclude cases pairwise"
msgstr "成對排除法"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid ""
"If one observation from a variable is missing, all the other variable "
"observations from the same case will still be used for the analysis. In this "
"scenario, it is not necessary to have an observation for all the variables "
"to include the case in the analysis. This option is selected by default."
msgstr ""
"若某個變項的觀測值遺失，該案例中其他變項的觀測值仍會被用於分析。在此情況下，"
"不需要所有變項皆有觀測值即可將該案例納入分析。此選項為預設選取。"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid "Exclude cases listwise"
msgstr "完全排除法"

msgctxt "PcaEfaOutputOptions|"
msgid ""
"If one observation from a variable is missing, the whole case, so all the "
"other connected variable observations, will be dismissed from the analysis. "
"In this scenario, observations for every variable are needed to include the "
"case in the analysis. "
msgstr ""
"若某變項之任一觀察值缺失，則該案例（即該案例所有其他相關變項之觀察值）將自分"
"析中排除。在此情況下，需所有變項均有觀察值，該案例方能納入分析。 "

